For pensioners, an insurance at any risk with franchise is preferable (i.e. 150 euros), or an extended insurance to third parties when the insurer has a high level of subsidy.
It must be said that car insurance is something important, not only because it covers the driver in the face of possible damages, but also because it represents an important expenditure, that is why it is essential for us to study the insurance that is most appropriate to our personal situation.
